Symbol.Script_UI:
!iVaultType VAULT_BARREL = 1 VAULT_3CENTERED = 2 VAULT_CROSS = 3 VAULT_DOMINICAL = 4 VAULT_CROSS_2 = 5 VAULT_3CENTCROSS = 6

dim stInfVault[] stInfVault[1] = `С одной стороны` stInfVault[2] = `Обе Стороны`

ui_page TABID_DIMENSIONS, TABID_ROOT, dimensionTabTitle, dimensionTabPict gosub "dimensionsPage"
ui_page TABID_REPRES, TABID_ROOT, `Отображение и Покрытия`, "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" gosub "AppearancePage"

"dimensionsPage":
x1 = 0 x2 = 120 x3 = 210 x4 = x2 + 100 x5 = x2 + 200 !200 (Style Guide => fillTypeInfLenght) x6 = 360 x7 = 408 xEnd = 444

ui_separator 0, yCurrent, xEnd, yCurrent

uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

ui_infield "A", uiPictX+100, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Длина Свода`
ui_infield "shell_thk", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY-5, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Свода` if iVaultType = VAULT_BARREL then ui_infield "radius_1", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+45, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Внешний Радиус Свода` endif
if iVaultType = VAULT_3CENTERED then ui_infield "B", uiPicLeftStart, uiPictY+45, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Ширина Свода` ui_infield "ZZYZX", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+45, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота Свода` ui_infield "radius_1", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+89, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Радиус Меньшей Окружности` endif endif

uiPicLeftStart = uiPictX - uiPictInfWdt - uiPictMargin uiPicLeftEND = uiPicLeftStart - uiPictMargin

uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

ui_infield "ZZYZX", uiPicLeftStart, uiPictY+20, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота` ui_infield "thicknessA", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY-5, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина над Аркой A` ui_infield "radiusA", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+20, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Радиус Арки A`

uiPicTop = uiPictY - uiPictMargin - infieldHeight + 3
uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

ui_infield "B", uiPicLeftStart, uiPictY+53, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Ширина Свода` ui_infield "A", uiPictX+32, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Длина Свода` ui_infield "offsetX", uiPictX+32, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Смещение Арки A (X)` ui_infield "offsetY", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+53, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Смещение Арки B (Y)`
uiPictX = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictInfWdt + uiPictMargin
uiPictWdt = 54 uiPictHgt = 125 uiPictMargin = 5 infieldHeight = 19
uiPicLeftStart = uiPictX - uiPictInfWdt - uiPictMargin uiPicLeftEND = uiPicLeftStart - uiPictMargin
uiPicTop = uiPictY - uiPictMargin - infieldHeight + 3
uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

ui_infield "radiusB", uiPictX-65, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Радиус Арки B` ui_infield "thicknessB", uiPictX+30, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина над Аркой B`
endif
if iVaultType = VAULT_DOMINICAL then uiPictX = 140 uiPictY = 10 uiPictWdt = 172 uiPictHgt = 242 uiPictMargin = 5 uiPictInfWdt = 60 infieldHeight = 19

uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

yCurrent = yCurrent + dy
ui_infield{3} "gs_f_simm", x1, yCurrent, xEnd-x1, infieldHeight, 7, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, "", `Симметричные Внутренние Своды`, 0, "", `Симметричные Внутренние Своды`, 1
yCurrent = yCurrent + dy
ui_separator 0, yCurrent-2, xEnd, yCurrent-2
uiPictX = 95 uiPictY = 73 uiPictWdt = 253 uiPictHgt = 171 uiPictMargin = 5 uiPictInfWdt = 90 infieldHeight = 19
uiPicLeftStart = uiPictX - uiPictInfWdt - uiPictMargin uiPicLeftEND = uiPicLeftStart - uiPictMargin
uiPicTop = uiPictY - uiPictMargin - infieldHeight + 3
uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin - 3
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin
if iVaultType = VAULT_CROSS_2 then if not(gs_f_simm) then if gs_f_type_m = 1 then ui_pict 11, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 else ui_pict 9, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 endif else if gs_f_type_m = 2 then ui_pict 10, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 else ui_pict 12, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 endif endif else if not(gs_f_simm) then if gs_f_type_m = 1 then ui_pict 15, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 else ui_pict 13, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 endif else if gs_f_type_m = 2 then ui_pict 14, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 else ui_pict 16, uiPictX , uiPictY , uiPictWdt , uiPictHgt , 1 endif endif endif

ui_infield "gs_shell_thk2", uiPictX+60, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Внутренних Сводов` if iVaultType = VAULT_CROSS_2 then ui_infield "gs_radius_2", uiPictX+153, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Внешний Радиус Внутренних Сводов` else ui_infield "gs_h2", uiPictX+153, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота Внутреннего Свода` ui_infield "gs_radius_2", uiPictX+246, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP _stSmallerRad endif
if not(gs_f_simm) then ui_infield "gs_firstaxis", uiPictX+5, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Расстояние Оси Первого Свода` endif
ui_infield "gs_ax_length", uiPictX+110, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Расстояние Осей Внутренних Сводов`
ui_infield "shell_thk", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+25, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Основного Свода` if iVaultType = VAULT_CROSS_2 then ui_infield "radius_1", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+75, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Внешний Радиус Основного Свода` else ui_infield "gs_h1", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+75, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота Основного Свода` ui_infield "radius_1", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+120, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP _stSmallerRad endif
endif
